ossibilities. Are you?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Software Testers are an integral member of AVEVA Global Licensing team responsible to test both Cloud based and on-premises licensing solutions. We provide our customers hassle-free license administration and usage reporting.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">As a Software Tester, you will be working closely with Architects, product owners, Developers and other colleagues. You will take a proactive approach to understanding the licensing business models we support.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">&nbsp;Engineering Graduates/Postgraduates in Mechanical/Chemical/ Civil/Electrical/Marine/Computer streams with first class degree.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- 5+ years of experience in Software Product Quality Assurance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Expertise in both API and UI testing.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Expertise in Software product quality and testing methodologies.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Excellent understanding and ability to develop tests, run tests, find defects and log defects effectively.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Expertise in Test Management and Testing Tools.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Ability to design, build, test and deploy effective test automation solutions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Have good knowledge on Automation Frameworks (Selenium, TestStack White, etc).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience in Test script development using C#, or other scripting languages.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience in designing automation frameworks for both Web and API.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Different phases of testing: systems integration, systems testing &amp; user acceptance testing.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Good understanding of development/test processes</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Clearly report test status with metrics, covering test development, execution and defects status.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Ability to estimate and plan testing and create structured Test Plans and Test Reports.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience of using Agile methodologies</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Excellent communication skills and self-motivated problem solver.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience in continuous integration and continuous deployment environments.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"></p>\n','\"<$>Role: Automation Test Engineer<$>Industry Type: IT Services & Consulting<$>Department: Engineering - Software & QA<$>Employment Type: Full Time, Permanent<$>Role Category: Quality Assurance and Testing\"','3,4,5,9','2,15',NULL,NULL,1,'Software Testing',_binary '',NULL,'2023-09-07 20:48:45','GDS_Recruiter1'),(20,'POS74966','QE Automation Engineer','Texas','Remote','<p style=\"text-align:left;\">&nbsp;Engineering Graduate\'s/Postgraduate\'s in Mechanical/Chemical/ Civil/Electrical/Marine/Computer streams with first class degree.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- 5+ years of experience in Software Product Quality Assurance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Expertise in both API and UI testing.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Expertise in Software product quality and testing methodologies.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Excellent understanding and ability to develop tests, run tests, find defects and log defects effectively.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Expertise in Test Management and Testing Tools.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Ability to design, build, test and deploy effective test automation solutions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Have good knowledge on Automation Frameworks (Selenium, TestStack White, etc).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience in Test script development using C#, or other scripting languages.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience in designing automation frameworks for both Web and API.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Different phases of testing: systems integration, systems testing &amp; user acceptance testing.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Good understanding of development/test processes</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Clearly report test status with metrics, covering test development, execution and defects status.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Ability to estimate and plan testing and create structured Test Plans and Test Reports.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience of using Agile methodologies</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Excellent communication skills and self-motivated problem solver.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">- Experience in continuous integration and continuous deployment environments.</p>\n','\"<$>Excellent understanding and ability to develop tests, run tests, find defects and log defects effectively.<$>Ability to design, build, test and deploy effective test automation solutions.\"','3,4,5,2,15','16,17,18,19',NULL,NULL,1,'Software Testing',_binary '',NULL,'2023-09-09 10:35:06','GDS_Recruiter1'),(21,'POS57382','Trainer','Texas','Onsite','<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\">Key Responsibilities : a: Ensure to develop and support the applications, acting as the primary interface between client and Accenture teams b: Can accurately define a client issue and can interpret and support a resolution based on deep product development and support knowledge c: Work with development and support team members to identify business requirements and different application development e: Finalize Strategy for Interfaces, Conversions, Report and Extension</li>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\">Technical Experience : a: Should have in depth knowledge on JavaScript, HTML, CSS, fundamentals and problem solving skill should be strong b: Should have knowledge on unit testing c: Should have knowledge on Library or Framework: ReactJs 1st, Vue, Angular At least one of the latest frameworks with hands on experience d: Good to have skills: Cloud